                        </div>
                        <div class="principle">
                            <p>
                                <span>Druhvi Patel, </span>Business Administration Major, Penn State Scranton, Class of 2022                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="impact">
                            <h2>Quick Fact:</h2><p>One in four Penn State students is a first-generation student.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row small-video-wrap" style="position: relative">
                    </div>
